article.description: — Kamdyn Curfman had 23 points and Honor Huff added 21 points as VMI beat Samford 99-80 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Curfman lifts VMI past Samford 99-80
article.story: LEXINGTON, Va. -- — Kamdyn Curfman had 23 points and Honor Huff added 21 points as VMI beat Samford 99-80 on Thursday night. Trey Bonham had 16 points and eight assists for VMI (11-8, 4-3 Southern Conference). Tanner Mans added 14 points. Logan Dye had 19 points and eight rebounds for the Bulldogs (11-7, 1-5). Ques Glover added 18 points and Jaron Rillie had 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
